description: LibOptimization is collection of optimization algorithms for .NET Framework. LibOptimization facilitate optimization using C#, VisualBasic.Net and other .Net Frametwork language. Implementing optimization algorithm are Steepest Descent Method, Newton Method, Nelder Mead Method (Down-Hill simplex method) ,Hooke and Jeeves of Pattern Search (Direct Search), Real-coded Genetic Algorithm(Simplex and JGG, REX and JGG) and Particle Swarm Optimization(Basic PSO, LDIW-PS, CDIW-PSO, CRIW-PSO, AIW-PSO).
releaseNotes: fix minor modification. add LDIW-PSO, CDIW-PSO, CRIW-PSO.
